snippet.title: Destiny 2: Shadowkeep – Season of the Undying Trailer
snippet.description:
The gateways have opened. The Vex are coming.

The Garden of Salvation is only the beginning. Season of the Undying, Destiny 2: Shadowkeep’s first seasonal content offering, starts on October 1, 2019. All purchases of Destiny 2: Shadowkeep include a Season Pass.

Destiny 2: Shadowkeep launches October 1.

PRE-ORDER SHADOWKEEP: bung.ie/Buy
